htw.vs1.filesystem.FileSystem.virtual

Interface Folder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FSObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalFolder, MountPointFolder, RemoteFolder

    public interface Folder
extends FSObject
    A Folder represents a node in our file system. It can either be a LocalFolder or a RemoteFolder. Created by markus on 01.06.15.
